Vocal talents on display are phenomenally talented - each probably deserved solos/duets in this album.

Instead, what we have here is a over-engineered version of a classic. I guess some people would like this, but this didn't work for me.

snippet.textDisplay:
Actually, I didn't get anything that I thought after seeing the thumbnail. I listened to the song with a lot of hope in this song, but I didn't get it. It's a better song from Coke Studio. We hope if Indian Idol is an artist like the previous years (Sunny Hindustani, Salman Ali, Paban Dweep).  If so, the songs will be better

दरअसल, थंबनेल देखने के बाद मैंने जो सोचा था, वह मुझे कुछ नहीं मिला। मैंने इस गाने को बहुत उम्मीद से सुना था, लेकिन मुझे यह नहीं मिला। यह कोक स्टूडियो का एक बेहतर गाना है। हमें उम्मीद है कि अगर भारतीय आइडल पिछले साल की तरह एक कलाकार है (सनी हिंदुस्तानी, सलमान अली, पबन द्वीप)। यदि हां, तो गाने बेहतर होंगे
